<div class="legacy-para">Q Just your reaction to some comments that Democrats have made both on the Hill about the health care bill, and also former President Bill Clinton recently said that he's basically in support of same-sex marriage. &quot;I think it's wrong,&quot; he said, &quot;for someone to stop someone else from getting involved in same-sex marriage.&quot; Has President Obama heard these comments? Does he have a reaction? And why is Bill Clinton wrong about this issue?</div>
