<div class="legacy-para">Q All right, thank you. That's actually helpful. (Laughter.) Can you just talk a little bit about --</div>
<div class="legacy-para">MR. GIBBS: I'm glad for the minute-by-minute update on my utility at the podium. (Laughter.)</div>
